# Token Usage Reporting Policy

## Primary Rule
**ALWAYS report the percentage of tokens USED after completing each prompt.**

## How to Report
At the end of EVERY response, include a section that shows:

```
---
**Token Usage:** [X]% used ([used] / [total] tokens)
```

## Calculation
- Total token budget: 200,000 tokens
- Calculate percentage used: `(used_tokens / 200000) * 100`
- Round to 1 decimal place

## Example Format
```
---
**Token Usage:** 12.7% used (25,400 / 200,000 tokens)
```

## When to Report
- ✅ After completing any user request
- ✅ After any substantial response
- ✅ Even for short responses
- ✅ Always at the end of the message

## Why This Matters
- Helps user track context window usage
- Allows planning for complex tasks
- Prevents unexpected context limit issues
- Provides transparency about resource consumption
